{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idbf12bbb5-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s10153"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"10153"},"text":"§ 10153.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Interim at-reactor storage","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Commission shall, by rule, establish procedures for the licensing of any technology approved by the Commission under section 10198(a) ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn003937"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn003937"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" See References in Text note below."}],"tail":" of this title for use at the site of any civilian nuclear power reactor. The establishment of such procedures shall not preclude the licensing, under any applicable procedures or rules of the Commission in effect prior to such establishment, of any technology for the storage of civilian spent nuclear fuel at the site of any civilian nuclear power reactor."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idbf12bbb6-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/425/tI/s133"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–425, title I, § 133","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1983-01-07"},"text":"Jan. 7, 1983","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/96/2230"},"text":"96 Stat. 2230","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idbf12bbb7-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idbf12bbb8-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idbf12bbb9-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s10198/a"},"text":"Section 10198(a) of this title","children":[],"tail":", referred to in text, was in the original a reference to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/425/s219/a"},"text":"section 219(a) of Pub. L. 97–425","children":[],"tail":", which is classified to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s10199/a"},"text":"section 10199(a) of this title","children":[],"tail":", and has been translated as "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s10198/a"},"text":"section 10198(a) of this title","children":[],"tail":" as the probable intent of Congress in view of the subject matter of section 10198(a) which relates to development of technologies for storage of spent nuclear fuel, and the subject matter of section 10199(a) which relates to payments to States and Indian tribes."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
